data.description: Completely remodeled 4 bedroom 3 bath home on almost 1 full acre. Updates include a new roof, new HVAC, new flooring and fixtures throughout the entire home. The kitchen boasts new cabinets, new stainless steel appliances, and a custom 12' island with granite and butcher block countertops. The residence offers a huge great room with split floor plan, great for peaceful family living. The master is spacious with plenty of closet space to meet everyone's needs. The home offers 4 bedroom and 2.5 baths with a den that could be used as another bedroom. If you are looking for land in a private setting but close to dining and shopping, this is the place for you! No HOA or CDD! Well water and septic will reduce utility payments. This lot is open and spacious while offering the security of being fully fenced in.  The entry gate is automated with keypad or remote entry.  Enjoy the mature trees on this lot from the beautiful covered porch off of the living room, or the front patio that leads to a 250 sq ft concrete block storage building and parking pad.  Call to schedule your showing today.
